projects.title: Interactify

projects.title: Cricket Win Predictor
projects.description: Leveraged Python and data science libraries to develop a model for predicting cricket match outcomes. Analyzed historical datasets of over 100,000 rows for pattern recognition and insights.

projects.title: Game Store Mobile Application
projects.description: Designed and built a cross-platform app for online game sales using Flutter and Firebase. Implemented user authentication and real-time database functionalities.

projects.title: Hospital Networking Topology
projects.description: Engineered a hospital networking topology featuring dynamic routing to interconnect the main branch with its sub-branches. Focused on optimizing communication and data transfer efficiency between various departments, demonstrating skills in network design and management.
